title: Week 16 Recap 2021
description:
Field Yates, Matthew Berry, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp recap all of the key fantasy takeaways from Week 16 including what trends you can trust for the rest of the fantasy playoffs. Plus, we give some updates on key injuries around the league.
